p.cl:
With these witnesses: namely, the lord J(ocelin) bishop of Glasgow; Arnold abbot
                  of Rievaulx; Simon archdeacon of Glasgow; John of Huntingdon;
                  William son of John; Roger of Berkeley; Richard le Neym;
                  Henry of Mow; Adam of Chatto; Ralph of Ryedale; Adam . . .
                  Alexander son of Waldef of Lilliesleaf; and many others.
